class TopRatedMovies extends Component<Props, State>{
    state: State = {
      status: 'LOADING',
      movies: [],
      error: Error
    };
    render() {
        let el;
        const { status, movies, error } = this.state;

        switch (status) {
            case 'LOADING':
                el = (
                    <LoadingIndicator
                        size="large"
                        message="We are loading movies, please wait.."
                    />
                );
                break;
            case 'LOADED':
                el = (
                    <Row xs={1} md={2} lg={3}>
                        {
                            movies.map(
                                movie => (
                                    <Col key={movie.title}>
                                        <MovieListItemTopRatedIndian
                                            movieIndia={movie} />
                                    </Col>
                                )
                            )
                        }
                    </Row>
                );
                break;
            case 'ERROR_LOADING':
                el = (
                    <Alert variant="danger">
                        {error.message}
                    </Alert>
                );
                break;
        }
        return el;
    }
    componentDidMount(){
        setTimeout(()=> {
           this.setState({
                status: 'LOADED',
                movies: movies
           });
        },3000);
    }
}

export default TopRatedMovies;
